Issues.Body:
This PR adds support for literal values inside the `--value('‚Ä¶')` and `--modifier('‚Ä¶')` functions. This allows you to safelist some known values you want to use:

E.g.:

```css
@utility tab-* {
  tab-size: --value('revert', 'initial');
}
```

This allows you to use `tab-revert` and `tab-initial` for example.
